tp://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"4 years ago","ctime":"April 8 2013, 13:45:49 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Roger Ebert","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://www.facebook.com/alan.ziebarth","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/facebook-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"Alan Ziebarth","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"ext_1744916","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://www.livejournal.com/profile?userid=62663146&t=I","alias":0}],"dname":"Alan Ziebarth","ctime_ts":1365428749,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/319625.html?thread=17552521#t17552521","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/319625.html?thread=17552521#t17552521","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/319625.html?thread=17552521#t17552521","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"matthew_at","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://matthew-at.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":17552521,"talkid":68564,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/319625.html?thread=17552521#t17552521","upictitle":"matthew_at: pic#0","article":"I agree that Roger Ebert was a great writer, and I often relied on his opinions when it came to deciding which movies to watch, but the thing about him that really stuck out was the sheer volume of his work. He watched and reviewed more than 300 movies a year! And he never fell back into a formula for his reviews so he could crank them out. (Plus he blogged on a number of topics, adding to his workload). ","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"4 years ago","ctime":"April 8 2013, 17:56:41 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"Great writer","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://matthew-at.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"matthew_at","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"matthew_at","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://matthew-at.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"matthew_at","ctime_ts":1365443801,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/120545379/62672658","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/319625.html?thread=17553033#t17553033","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/319625.html?thread=17553033#t17553033","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/319625.html?thread=17553033#t17553033","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"ext_1745604","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://twitter.com/cecyrobson","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":17553033,"talkid":68566,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/319625.html?thread=17553033#t17553033","upictitle":"cecyrobson: pic#120545379","article":"I'm with you. I was glued to AT THE MOVIES as a kid. And you're right, while I didn't always share his opinion, his intelligence and personality always shined.  He was also fair, and while he could be critical, I don't ever remember him being mean. RIP, Roger. You get my thumbs up.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"4 years ago","ctime":"April 8 2013, 20:08:59 UTC","massactions":0,"subject":"So sad.","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://twitter.com/cecyrobson","striked":null,"journaltype":"I","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/icons/twitter-16.png?v=29916?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"cecyrobson","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":1,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"